{"tid":1132943,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[劇透] Russo Brother接受EW訪問回應Endgame結局疑問","createTime":"2019-04-30T16:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T04:48:11.000Z","uid":34123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d52c831ae6d468929080b0088414e9702adb1376","tid":1132943,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ew.com/movies/2019/04/30/avengers-endgame-russo-brothers-captain-america/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Few.com%2Fmovies%2F2019%2F04%2F30%2Favengers-endgame-russo-brothers-captain-america%2F&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1UpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=563cd2c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://ew.com/movies/2019/04/30/avengers-endgame-russo-brothers-captain-america/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBucky<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f41667c55d51405a5ff5e250ab0347d53e73d8c","tid":1132943,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"So, has Cap&nbsp;been living in the past this whole time&nbsp;&mdash; or did he go and live in another dimension?<br />\n<br />\nThe directors say it&rsquo;s the latter.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;If Cap were to go back into the past and live there, he would create a branched reality,&rdquo; Joe explained. &ldquo;The question then becomes, how is he back in&nbsp;this&nbsp;reality to give the shield away?&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\nThe brothers smile.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Interesting question, right?&rdquo; Joe said. &ldquo;Maybe there&rsquo;s a story there. There&rsquo;s a lot of layers built into this movie and we spent three years thinking through it, so it&rsquo;s fun to talk about it and hopefully fill in holes for people so